PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F348A1674627992
OL,6,FWhatever happened behind-the-scenes,
OL,7,Fthe subsequent changes into BBC
OL,8,FBreakfast News in 1989 and Breakfast in
OL,9,Fits modern form in 2000 seemed
OL,10,Fevolutionary from the viewer's
OL,11,Fperspective. There was no great
OL,12,Fcontroversy on either occasion.
OL,14,FAfter 2000 the atmosphere gradually got
OL,15,Fwarmer and that old friendly atmosphere
OL,16,Fwas restored.
OL,18,FBreakfast today is a news programme
OL,19,Frooted in the BBC's journalism.
OL,3,CReflections on the history of BBC
OL,4,Cbreakfast TV
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G5/6
