PN,34806
SC,0006
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F348A1674627992
OL,6,FBut that friendliness and closeness to
OL,7,Fits audience is a tribute to the
OL,8,Foriginal Breakfast Time.
OL,10,FPerhaps the proof the pioneers got the
OL,11,Fbasic style of presentation right came
OL,12,F20 years ago when Breakfast overtook
OL,13,FGMTV in the ratings.
OL,15,FIf only somebody in 1986 had realised
OL,16,Fthat revamping the content did not mean
OL,17,Fbreaking the relationship with the
OL,18,Faudience. Serious does not mean cold or
OL,19,Fimpersonal.
OL,3,CReflections on the history of BBC
